name: REFRACT - The GIFs - GIF-r11/48
description:
GIF 11 of 48.

This GIF is part of C3 along with GIF-r10 and GIF-r12. First 11 collectors to complete C3 will be awarded with 1 edition of OBJKT#XXXXXX (to be revealed on Oct 7th).

First 11 collectors to complete the serie will be awarded with 1 edition of REFRACT -AV- (to be revealed on Oct 8th). 

Items from this collection will be minted and swaped once a day from Aug 20th to Oct 6th.
